org.apache.edgent.test.svt.apps

Class FleetManagementAnalyticsClientApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.edgent.samples.apps.AbstractApplication
      • org.apache.edgent.test.svt.apps.iotp.AbstractIotpApplication
        • org.apache.edgent.test.svt.apps.FleetManagementAnalyticsClientApplication

  • public class FleetManagementAnalyticsClientApplication
extends AbstractIotpApplication
    A Global Positional System and On-Board Diagnostics application to perform analytics defined in GpsAnalyticsApplication and ObdAnalyticsApplication.

    The Edgent console URL is written to the console and to file consoleUrl.txt.

    The Watson IotF URL is written to the console and to file iotfUrl.txt

    Argument: specify pathname to application properties file. If running in Eclipse, you can specify GpsObdAnalyticsApplication.properties.
